videos.headline: Car's 37-yard TD run puts Houston on the board first
videos.description: Mulbah Car finds an opening and breaks into the end zone for a 37-yard Cougars touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Car's 37-yard TD run puts Houston on the board first) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Gabriel, Williams connect for 6-yard UCF score
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel finds Marln Williams for a 6-yard touchdown to get UCF on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Gabriel, Williams connect for 6-yard UCF score) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Gabriel finds Nixon for a 32-yard TD
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel goes deep to Tre Nixon for a 32-yard UCF touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Gabriel finds Nixon for a 32-yard TD) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Gabriel fools defenders, runs in for TD
videos.description: UCF QB Dillon Gabriel fakes a handoff and takes it to the house himself to give UCF the lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Gabriel fools defenders, runs in for TD) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Thompson takes it to the house for a 43-yard TD
videos.description: Bentavious Thompson takes off and finds the end zone for a 43-yard Golden Knights touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Thompson takes it to the house for a 43-yard TD) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Gabriel, Nixon connect for another scoring strike
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel finds a wide-open Tre Nixon for a 34-yard UCF touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Gabriel, Nixon connect for another scoring strike) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Singleton makes clutch grab in the corner of the end zone
videos.description: Clayton Tune finds Jeremy Singleton, who reaches out for the catch and is able to pull the ball back into the end zone for a Houston touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Singleton makes clutch grab in the corner of the end zone) 2019/11/02
